Constructor & Destructor Documentation

template<class _Tp >
fc_queue< _Tp >::fc_queue (  )  [inline]

Default constructor that creates a null queue.

The queue remains in an uninitialized (capacity not set), though defined, state. The member functions empty(), full(), capacity(), and size() still return meaningful results.
